{"tid":2375976,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"六人涉新城市廣場和你Sing違限聚令 「霸氣哥」同日兩度票控分案審理","createTime":"2021-01-22T12:07:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T15:24:54.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"50c141db541a6a00210fb5a06f3462425126c48c","tid":2375976,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T12:07:46.000Z","msg":"去年5月1日勞動節，網民號召到沙田新城市廣場「和你Sing」，其間六名人士被票控違反限聚令，人稱「霸氣哥」的曾建峰同日更被兩度票控。六人今在沙田裁判法院提堂，將分兩案進行審訊。其中曾建峰面對的兩張傳票亦被分開處理，意味着須面對兩次審訊。<br />\n<br />\n控方指曾、鄭及宋三人涉案的地點相同，由於牽涉同一事情，證人相同，故要求將此三人的案件合併處理。此外，曾在另一地點被票控，與梁、連及楊的案發地點相約，控方遂申請此4人的案件合併處理。首案押後至2月23日進行審前覆核，次案則排期至5月20日開審。<br />\n<br />\n鄭一度反對與別人一同受審，以「我又唔識佢兩個，唔想聽人哋啲私隱」為由反對，辯方亦質疑控方未有提出任何證據證明各被告案件互有關係。惟裁判官香淑嫻最終裁定案件結合處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210122/KXUUSIHAWFCUBGI3ONDEDRGGQQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210122%2FKXUUSIHAWFCUBGI3ONDEDRGGQQ%2F&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TXHr90zhVRml9IH8Z62du0k%3D&h=7efa4ef1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210122%2FKXUUSIHAWFCUBGI3ONDEDRGGQQ%2F&h=1ef6d87c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210122/KXUUSIHAWFCUBGI3ONDEDRGGQQ/</a>"},{"pid":"4bd93cfd7daf4e25493d52d2abdc2a26c993bc1d","tid":2375976,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T12:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de6f3bec5d29c03cc623f049934c8080ed049d54","tid":2375976,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T12:33:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337c128